item.title: CVE-2020-2259|2024-08-04T07:01:41.206Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20computer-queue-plugin%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins computer-queue-plugin Plugin 1.5 and earlier does not escape the agent name in tooltips, resulting in a stored cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability exploitable by attackers with Agent/Configure permission.
